abstract: WNBA Roundup; Indiana Fever beats New York Liberty, 70-64 in Game 2 of WNBA Eastern Conference finals; other basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Down 15 points at halftime, Indiana put together a 21-4 run led by Tamika Catchings that stunned the Liberty and sent the Eastern Conference finals to a decisive Game 3.

headline.main: Rally by Fever in 2nd Half Evens Series With Liberty
